    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it still looks and smells brand new. It drives like a dream and has been kept tucked away in the garage. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
