    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s specimen, preserved in absolute showroom condition. The exterior boasts its original deep-gloss factory finish, completely free of swirls, rock chips, or imperfections, having been professionally ceramic coated and strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather still retains its factory-fresh scent, with absolutely no bolster wear, carpet staining, or sun-fading on the dashboard. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, performing with the same tight, responsive precision as the day it left the factory. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive, chronological binder of maintenance records included in the sale. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the smallest ambient light, functions perfectly. From the spotless engine bay to the pristine undercarriage, this car is indistinguishable from a brand-new vehicle. It is ready for a discerning owner who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
